<plot>ALLEEN is number 28 of the 34 BOY MEETS GIRL STORIES: Cinematographic representations of the thoughts and feelings people have when they are in love. The recognizable short films are without explanation or definition. They are more poems of the unqualified feelings of being in love, filmed in a characteristic way. The 34 short films are connected by the search of Milou who believes that everybody has 7 chances to meet the right one.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?081083</url></doc>
